<title>Set the Name and Description of a Deployment Package</title>

Every deployment package must have a name. This should be a short title of the application contained in the package. The name will be displayed in the list of available applications for download on the mobile device. Enter the name of the package in the text box next to <b>Package Name</b>.

You may also add an optional description of the package. This may be longer than the package name offering additonal details about the application package. It will be displayed underneath the name in the list of available applications for download on the mobile device. Enter the package description in the text box next to <b>Description</b>.

